BEGIN NOW Rotating scenes of razor-sharp blades dissecting through my mind. END
BEGIN NOW I contemplate the nature of fear in all its manifestations--here there is true, unmitigated terror. END
BEGIN NOW A woman reaches back and rips the top part of her skull off; a horde of black moths flies out. END
BEGIN NOW I hear the whispering voices of angels. END
BEGIN NOW Cut. END
BEGIN NOW I lift my eyelids and stare into the darkness of my room to find relief from the torrential deluge of demonic imagery. END
